Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\N but then a small incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I believed in was my courageous heart.\N What I gained were magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wished for was that even my\N smallest feelings would reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The start of every new journey is always full of sadness,\N but because our feelings are surely connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye" isn't a word of finality, but\N rather the word of a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please! Escape! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly... towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call My Name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the earthquake's stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Garden has completely collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything within it has been absorbed\N into the imaginary dark spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the dimensional disturbance\N has been prevented.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no indication of a\N dimensional dislocation outbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Returning to level three nautical velocity,\N and resuming our normal patrol cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Fate-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Arf in the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's a vital witness for this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this, but she'll be held\N in isolation for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way- ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha! Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had made a mistake with this incident, a\N dimensional dislocation would probably have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very grave matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the\N Time-Space Administration Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't afford to treat anyone\N related to this case leniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amy, fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And after that, a lot of things finally ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the day I met Yuuno-kun to today when\N everything ended, it seems like the time just flew by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While the aftereffects of the dimensional\N disturbance were being repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...we remained aboard the Asura for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been a great number of meritorious deeds\N involved with the conclusion of this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll have to summarize them for now,\N but I give them all my highest praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamachi Nanoha-san, Yuuno Scrya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono-kun... what's going to\N happen to Fate-chan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even under the circumstances, she can't deny that she\N was an accomplice in the dimensional interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because this is a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the punishment for this would be\N imprisonment for a couple hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is unique this time, and it's clear that\N she didn't willingly participate in the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's really left is getting the\N higher-ups to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm confident in my ability\N to do that, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time-Space Administration Bureau isn't so cold as\N to question a girl who unknowingly committed a sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when she was simply trying her\N best to fulfill her mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono-kun, are you really a nice\N person underneath everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-As a government official, it's only\N natural to make such a remark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm voicing my own opinions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so embarrassed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not being embarrassed about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBF6281&}He's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The residual effects of the dimensional\N disturbance should settle down soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From where we stand now, I can safely say that we\N should be able to return you to your world tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for you... the space around Midchilda is still\N extremely unstable and hasn't equalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it looks like it'll take some time until it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's going to take a couple months or even\N a half a year until that area becomes safe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well, my tribe does nothing but\N search for new relics and artifacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I don't think there's any need to hurry home, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't just stay here in your\N care the whole time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you stay at my house?\N Just like we've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha, is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! If it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, umm... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in your care once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, it's because you slept so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I was up all night\N working... I'm still so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that place she was aiming for,\N don't you, Yuuno-kun? Alhazred...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I heard of it once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it existed in space long ago before\N the old lunar calendar was established...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that it was a land filled with\N secret arts and technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also said it was destroyed during\N a dimensional dislocation long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that all magic arrives\N there in its ultimate form...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and if one were to hold that power,\N one's every wish could be granted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...through Alhazred's secret technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that would allow you to transcend\N the barriers of time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that would even let you rewrite your past...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that could bring someone back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some of the things she was seeking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone who studies magic knows two things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling back in time and reviving\N the deceased is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she wished for both things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she couldn't overlook the fact that it was\N nothing more than a fairy tale world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't bear the fact that it was simply a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... since that great mage risked her life in\N search of it, she might've actually found...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the path to Alhazred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we'll never know if she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I ended up going into a long discussion\N when we just sat down to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and eat up before the food gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this will probably be the last meal\N on the Asura for you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just say that you're sad about seeing her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono-kun, you're such a shy guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan, you can come over\N and play whenever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amy! The Asura isn't some playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, our patrols are always full of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even you, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then came the morning\N Yuuno-kun and I were to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... once again, thank you very much\N for all you've done in this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you once Fate's verdict is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be fine, though.\N I promise nothing bad will happen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun, if you ever want to return\N to your world, just let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a gate for you whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I guess it's time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you again, Chrono-kun, Amy-san, Lindy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we head home, Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\3c&H333F94&}And my everyday life had returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all should have gone back to how it used to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H333F94&}Mom! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but a lot of things happened, so it's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my famous yellowtail and white radish meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back. I came back just like I said I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think back on the time when I\N was busy working with Yuuno-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it feels like it all happened in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But those events certainly left an\N impression within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the people I met... each time I was at\N my wit's end... there's so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's been so long since I've slept in my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You be sure to sleep well tonight too, okay, Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And really, thanks a lot for everything\N you did, Raising Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work too, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though... the only thing I'm worried\N about now... is that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl who's so gentle...\N who has such beautiful eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a few days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! This is Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was just officially decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate will be taken into the custody of our main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing her description of the\N circumstances, a trial will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate will probably... no, I can almost definitely say\N she will be found innocent. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Chrono-kun personally\N saw to the case after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amy! You don't need to say unnecessary\N things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much, Chrono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the evidentiary hearing and trial will take\N some time to process, so before all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Fate will be transferred\N to their main office for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they said I could see her before they move her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even said she wanted to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time, but I think you\N guys should talk while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting on the other side, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much I wanted to talk\N to you about, but it's funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as soon as I saw your face, I completely forgot it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right... I can't put what\N I want to say into words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you faced me with such honesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... because I thought it'd be\N nice if we could become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... after today, you'll be leaving\N for a while, won't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... apparently, it will be a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely meet again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me a little sad, but... I'm finally\N able to start anew as my true self, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here today... to give you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To those words you said to me...\N "I want us to be friends..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought.. if I could do it... if it\N would be all right with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I... don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to tell me...\N how can we become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming friends with someone is really simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to call out her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you need to do at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "hey, you" or call her "that person," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look straight into her eyes and clearly say her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takamachi Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano... ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand sure is warm... Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I just learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see a friend crying, you also become sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to leave you for now, but...\N I'm sure we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we do... is it all right if I call your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I want to see you...\N I'll be sure to call out your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please call out my name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time when you're the one in trouble,\N I'm sure I'll be the one to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... Nanoha... is really such a good girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For her to make Fate smile that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time. Are you two about done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can give you...\N so I'll remain in your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you mine, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! You stay well too, okay, Arf-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks for everything you did, Nanoha, Yuuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll also be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Chrono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye... see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arf-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:16.58,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Little Wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:20.23,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.88,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,since you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:32.07,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:42.28,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's okay to keep going without hanging your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.28,0:23:45.88,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the courage you gave to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:49.77,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0001,,that day is still in this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,448)}Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,448)}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.77,0:23:53.46,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,As the stars begin to twinkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:57.06,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,kindness is born again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:00.67,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to always, always
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:05.39,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,cherish this love of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:09.27,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Little Wish and wrap
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:13.00,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,yourself in the lemon-colored drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:16.87,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:20.05,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:23.91,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Little Wish, on days when it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.91,0:24:27.57,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,or at dawn when you can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:31.41,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.41,0:24:38.05,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to have this great smile, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:46.10,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in times when we're far apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.10,0:24:49.77,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,there's always one thing I hold to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:53.44,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,That our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:58.17,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,are always, always one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.17,0:25:02.08,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Little Wish and gather
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:05.71,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,the lemon-colored drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.71,0:25:09.61,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Your warm tears will only
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.61,0:25:12.75,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,become the spice of my smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.75,0:25:16.59,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Little Wish, I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:20.26,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey, but
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.26,0:25:24.10,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,since you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:30.99,LyricsED,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
